Edward Hibbert https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edward_Hibbert 0 Edward Hibbert (born 9 September 1955) is an Anglo-American actor and literary agent. He played Gil Chesterton in the TV series Frasier. He also voiced Zazu in both The Lion King II: Simba's Pride and The Lion King 1½, replacing Rowan Atkinson. Edward_Hibbert ( born_9_September_1955 ) is an_Anglo-American_actor_and_literary_agent .
